Hi Block

3D Block

Data

HEK cells processed for S3EM (Os, UA, LA). 96 serial sections cut with Diatome knives on a Leica ultramicrotome, collected on a silicon chip. Imaged on a Zeiss SEM with 8-8-70 nm (x-y-z) voxels.

Interact

Select points on the PCA and click the Update Model button to see the corresponding mitochondria. PCs are generated from curvature, surface area, and volume parameters. Click Load Big Model button to load all mitos into a single scene (may take some time).
